{"tid":669023,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食評：銅鑼灣老雪園","createTime":"2018-05-18T06:42:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T08:20:08.000Z","uid":181719,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2d5bce10ac7812a36e848726b2f751dc7b708087","tid":669023,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T06:42:59.000Z","msg":"話說中意食上海菜嘅香港人，一定知道雪園呢個傳奇品牌，自從北角總店出名之後，香港多咗好多個名有「雪園」2個字嘅上海菜館，係唔係同一班底，都不得而知。今次呢一間，又聽講係北角雪園執笠之後原班人馬開嘅，行到落去都FEEL到貴。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/18/143609_32ca910b38de5358c7a1f1565eae174a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2F143609_32ca910b38de5358c7a1f1565eae174a.jpeg&h=302339a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/18/143628_4ef006bd67084eb2081d4a21b69e6445.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2F143628_4ef006bd67084eb2081d4a21b69e6445.jpeg&h=5a4f789d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然好貴，但咁出名點都要試一次架喇。都係果句，一個人食唔得多野，所以淨係叫咗個咸肉津白炒年糕，同埋一籠小籠包。<br />\n<br />\n上海咸肉，真係由細食到大嘅，唔同部位，唔同肥瘦都有唔同風味，但係對我黎講，首要就係唔好切絲甚至切粒先，因為體績太細，根本好難試清楚好唔好食。好喇，問清楚侍應係切片定係切絲定係切粒炒先啦，佢好肯定係切片架喎，咁咪叫囉，一上檯，仆你個街，點解係切絲嘅先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/18/143744_5cdc65da8548527916aeb477ca05d47f.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2F143744_5cdc65da8548527916aeb477ca05d47f.jpeg&h=88ed1e86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我就叫返個侍應黎問，大家望住碟野，鳩笑咗幾秒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n咁算啦，無謂難為人地，照食。個侍應之後仲問我好唔好食，真係攞景咩？其實真係好一般。大家食開炒年糕嘅話，會知道佢係分預先切好同餐廳自己切兩款嘅，後者係比較大塊同質感煙韌啲。呢度啲年糕屬於後者，炒功相當好，食咗半碟仍然有鑊氣，仲落咗筍絲吊味，令碟野口感冇咁寡。既然係咁，衰乜野呢？咸肉貨不對辦，頭先已經講過，仲有一個死症係，勁多油......<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/18/143806_1b181d5bd454754e5882e022ec847a32.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2F143806_1b181d5bd454754e5882e022ec847a32.jpeg&h=5f61d0d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食哂之後......<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/18/143834_0351b77c3a5c60b59e38830abbb11a99.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2F143834_0351b77c3a5c60b59e38830abbb11a99.jpeg&h=28be42dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於小籠包，44蚊籠喺呢度黎講算好平，蒸出黎，火侯稍為過咗，一睇啲包皮微微下陷就知架喇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/18/143909_56628454b0ebb517b7c8bba865d8bb41.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2F143909_56628454b0ebb517b7c8bba865d8bb41.jpeg&h=b2592a1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但食落肉餡好有鮮味，湯汁好多，影咗一張手殘相，睇到少少湯汁。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/18/143935_3437b382001116ceacba66235d90a449.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2F143935_3437b382001116ceacba66235d90a449.jpeg&h=b6802da2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n總括黎講，兩樣野，埋單超過200蚊，本來以酒店中菜館黎講唔算好過份，過份在佢貨不對辦啫。雪園最出名其實係生煎包，但1個人食唔落，下次會再黎試多次。"},{"pid":"e1c1582c5b3fe76d3de6031dc827bc72c8134737","tid":669023,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T08:08:16.000Z","msg":"切絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d82bf5439c18e4d33f103d1e882ca56788da06dd","tid":669023,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1c1582c5b3fe76d3de6031dc827bc72c8134737","tid":669023,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T08:08:16.000Z","msg":"切絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T08:20:08.000Z","msg":"其實最中意醃篤鮮切塊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過一個人食唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}